  "text": "Article was determined by the REMA (Resazurin Microtiter Assay) method. [CITATION_1] Stock solutions of the tested compounds (10 μg/mL) were prepared in DMSO and diluted in Middlebrook 7H9 broth supplemented with 10% OADC.",
